comment: a man in a striped blue shirt and a balloon hat is making other balloon animals
Translated Comment: судалтай цэнхэр цамцтай, бөмбөлөг малгай нь бусад бөмбөлөг амьтдыг гаргаж байна

comment: A young boy in a green shirt wearing a blue harness stares at a white dog in a red harness while taking a walk .

comment: Two male police officers are standing on a pier or sidewalk of a beach , with four females in the background and two green trash barrels and a bench .

comment: A lady playing a cello wearing a gold skirt with a green tuba player in front of her .

comment: Young boys in green and blue jerseys kick around a soccer ball while other soccer games take place in the background .

comment: A guy with his hand on his chin , tattoos on both arms , and a gold bracelet on standing behind a food business counter .

comment: A man in a turban sits prostrate with his boots on the ground in front of him .

comment: A man changing the tire and doing some maintenance on a bus , with someone assisting with the tires .

comment: A man is standing on a power post looking as though he is fixing a power line in a city .

comment: A woman in a white t-shirt and jeans standing on a Segway talking to two men
Translated Comment: Цагаан футболк, жинсэн өмд өмсөж буй эмэгтэй хоёр эрэгтэйтэй ярилцаж байна

comment: Pushing a mower that is a bit too large for him , a young boy tries to cut some grass .

comment: A person is directing traffic while repairs are being made at a telephone pole .

comment: A barefoot man in rainbow shorts and a green shirt completes a food purchase at an outdoor concession stand .

comment: Two older people in marching uniforms both playing saxophones .

comment: A group of people with colorful clothing walking down the street playing homemade instruments .

comment: A silhouette of a child playing in the beautiful ocean at sunset .

comment: A man is carrying a baby in a pouch to his chest is helping a small boy walk across a log by holding his hand .

comment: People marching down a street playing band instruments , a man in foreground is dressed like a baker .
